name: KICK01
description: The KICK series by CATEGORY FIVE is a love letter to the kick drum. The kick drum is the foundation of all music, the ruler of the rhythm. The KICK series is the first to implement the CATEGORY FIVE A/V PRODUCTION METHOD. The KICK series will be minted and available exclusively on hic et nunc. Only 10 of each edition will be minted.  KICK01: Synth - PO-12, Effects - Vibrato, BPM - 120, Time Signature - 4/4, Measures - 4
